title: U2 Medium, Rare & Remastered [EAC-FLAC]
description:
This is the last u2.com subscription gift: a double cd with lot of previously unreleased songs, some b-sides and some alternate version. Some of them were released only with the itunes box "the Complete U2" in compressed format... so this is the first nice gift from u2.com.
As usual, this is a perfect rip with EAC, with accurate rip match (I received theese original cds just today!): the torrent contain cuesheets, logs (even if they're embedded in the flac file) and an 800x800 scan of the front.
My upload speed is 10-15 kbyte/s until the 4th of may, then it will be around 400-500 kbyte/s (!!!), so be patient!

Here the tracklist, then the 2 logs, hope you enjoy!


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Disc: 1

    * Levitate
    * Love You Like Mad
    * Smile
    * Flower Child
    * Beautiful Ghost/Introduction To Songs Of Experience
    * Jesus Christ
    * Xanax And Wine
    * All Because Of You - (Early mix)
    * Native Son
    * Yahweh - (Early mix)
    * Sometimes You Can't Make It On Your Own - (Early mix) 

Disc: 2

    * Saturday Night
    * Trash, Trampoline And The Party Girl
    * Angels Too Tied To The Ground
    * Wave Of Sorrow (Birdland)
    * Always
    * Summer Rain
    * Big Girls Are Best
    * Neon Lights
    * Fast Cars
